ygData.subject: Re: DE Bards
ygData.msgSnippet: I think the Evil Race will be one of the more Formidable teams to fight against, mainly because they have access to some of the better dungeons in the game,
ygData.messageBody:
I think the Evil Race will be one of the more Formidable teams to fight
against, mainly because they have access to some of the better dungeons in
the game, this means that having Bards will put them at an even higher
advantage ) Befallen will be fought over alot.
----- Original Message -----
From: CMai <CMai@...>
To: Eqbards (E-mail) <eqbards@onelist.com>
Sent: Thursday, July 15, 1999 11:56 AM
Subject: [eqbards] DE Bards


From: CMai <CMai@...>

I think they should have a DE bards because of the Race War server. If the
dark side does not have a bard then they will be in a big disadvantage!
Unless you want the evil race to lose, hehe.

Your Friendly Rogue and Bard
Hammerpaw and Samiam Syren Wind
Champions of Norrath, The Rathe
